references: Related: CF 264263. Amending: Ord 90379, Ord 96301. Repealing: Ord 94452.
summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Garbage Utility; amending Sections 4, 4.1 and 5 of Ordinance 90379 to increase the rates and charges imposed for collection and disposal of garbage and rubbish, and repealing Ordinance 94452.
